          "date": "2014-05-04 22:37:42.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-4999 lustre: clean lustre_idl.h of internal defines",
        "message": "LU-4999 lustre: clean lustre_idl.h of internal defines\n\nIn lustre_idl.h replace CERROR() uses with LUSTRE_CERROR() which is\ndefined to be CERROR() when compiling lustre and ((void)0) otherwise\nand similarly for likely(), unlikely(). Convert uses of the LP{U,X}\nmacros to %ll{x,u} with explict casts. Replace calls to memcmp() with\nexplict comparisons.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ifb22865bfe3cc7b8f1c45225f54e6c511cc8e958\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
